text: Khanty-Mansiysk (, lit. Khanty-Mansi Town; Khanty: , Jomvoćś; Mansi: , Abga) is a city in Russia. It is the administrative center of Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug. In 2024, 111,772 people lived there. Category:Capitals of autonomous okrugs of Russia Category:Cities and towns in Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug
title: Khanty-Mansiysk
